  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "I think this Info Action is somewhat of a step in the right direction, but not quite a workable solution.  In my opinion we definitely need to figure out some way to separate planning and spending into two separate things.  That way the treasury withdrawals themselves end up being more of a formality to carry out the agreed-upon plan.  Splitting spending into different category buckets is one way of doing that, but I'm not sure how we get to that point simply from reading this info action.  Will vote ABSTAIN because I am not convinced one way or the other."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}